item.title: PeiKe Wang
item.description: Self Introduction My name is Peike Wang, a computer science and technology graduate student at Beijing University of Technology. I am currently in the $ \lfloor e\rfloor$ grade. The research direction is to optimize algorithms and neural architecture search. I am a native of Weinan, Shaanxi, and currently live in Beijing. I like math, astrophysics, and computer-related content. I play online games occasionally, but I am not good at sports, like food and movies. If I don’t go to school, I will stay at home because I don’t like to go outside (unless I go out with my girlfriend or go to the aquarium or museum).
